---
import BaseLayout from '../layouts/BaseLayout.astro';
---
<BaseLayout title={'Contact — Goldfin Group'} description={'Reach Goldfin Group. Inquiries are directed to our Client Service Director, Cat Lindsay. Offices in Franklin, Tennessee and Albuquerque, New Mexico — and we meet clients across the country over Zoom.'} path={'/contact'}>

<style>
  .contact-grid{display:grid;grid-template-columns:1fr 1fr;gap:18px;margin-bottom:18px}
  @media(max-width:720px){.contact-grid{grid-template-columns:1fr}}
  .office-card{padding:32px;border:1px solid rgba(40,39,40,.12);border-radius:3px;background:var(--bone-deep)}
  .office-card .city{font-size:11px;font-weight:700;letter-spacing:.2em;text-transform:uppercase;color:var(--gold-rich);margin-bottom:14px}
  .office-card .addr{font-family:var(--serif);font-size:19px;font-style:italic;line-height:1.5;color:var(--ink);font-weight:400}
  .office-card .addr span{display:block;font-family:var(--sans);font-style:normal;font-size:14px;font-weight:300;color:rgba(40,39,40,.7);margin-top:8px;letter-spacing:.01em}

  .reach-bar{display:grid;grid-template-columns:1fr;gap:0;background:var(--green-deep);border-radius:3px;overflow:hidden;margin-bottom:18px}
  .reach-head{padding:30px 32px 24px}
  .reach-head .eyebrow-sm{font-size:11px;font-weight:700;letter-spacing:.2em;text-transform:uppercase;color:var(--gold);margin-bottom:12px}
  .reach-head h2{font-family:var(--serif);font-style:italic;font-size:24px;font-weight:400;color:var(--bone);line-height:1.4;margin-bottom:10px}
  .reach-head p{font-weight:300;font-size:15px;color:rgba(246,241,231,.78);line-height:1.7;max-width:54ch}
  .reach-rows{display:grid;grid-template-columns:1fr 1fr;border-top:1px solid rgba(246,241,231,.12)}
  @media(max-width:560px){.reach-rows{grid-template-columns:1fr}}
  .reach-row{padding:24px 32px;display:flex;align-items:center;gap:16px}
  .reach-row + .reach-row{border-left:1px solid rgba(246,241,231,.12)}
  @media(max-width:560px){.reach-row + .reach-row{border-left:none;border-top:1px solid rgba(246,241,231,.12)}}
  .reach-row svg{flex-shrink:0}
  .reach-row .label{font-size:10px;font-weight:700;letter-spacing:.16em;text-transform:uppercase;color:rgba(246,241,231,.5);margin-bottom:4px}
  .reach-row a,.reach-row .val{font-family:var(--sans);font-size:17px;font-weight:400;color:var(--bone);text-decoration:none}
  .reach-row a:hover{color:var(--gold)}

  .director-note{display:flex;align-items:flex-start;gap:16px;padding:24px 28px;border-left:2px solid var(--gold);background:rgba(203,159,90,.06);border-radius:0 3px 3px 0;margin-bottom:40px}
  .director-note .dn-mark{font-family:var(--serif);font-style:italic;font-size:26px;color:var(--gold-rich);line-height:1;flex-shrink:0;margin-top:2px}
  .director-note p{font-family:var(--serif);font-style:italic;font-size:16px;line-height:1.65;color:var(--ink)}

  .scarcity{text-align:center;max-width:60ch;margin:0 auto 44px}
  .scarcity p{font-family:var(--serif);font-size:19px;font-style:italic;line-height:1.6;color:rgba(40,39,40,.82);font-weight:400}
  .scarcity .reach-line{font-family:var(--sans);font-style:normal;font-size:15px;font-weight:300;color:rgba(40,39,40,.7);margin-top:14px;line-height:1.7}
  .phase-label{font-size:11px;font-weight:700;letter-spacing:.28em;text-transform:uppercase;margin-bottom:1.25rem;display:flex;align-items:center;gap:12px;color:var(--gold-rich)}
  .phase-label::after{content:"";flex:1;height:1px;background:var(--gold);opacity:.3}
</style>

<div class="pagehead">
  <div class="wrap">
    <p class="eyebrow">Contact</p>
    <h1>Let's <em>start a conversation.</em></h1>
    <p class="lead">Whether you're years from a sale or staring at an offer, the first step is a conversation — no pitch, no pressure.</p>
  </div>
</div>

<section>
  <div class="wrap">

    <div class="reach-bar">
      <div class="reach-head">
        <p class="eyebrow-sm">Where to begin</p>
        <h2>All inquiries are welcomed by Cat Lindsay, our Client Service Director.</h2>
        <p>Cat is the first person you'll meet and the one who makes sure nothing falls through the cracks. Reach her directly, or simply book a 15-minute call and we'll take it from there.</p>
      </div>
      <div class="reach-rows">
        <div class="reach-row">
          <svg width="22" height="22" viewBox="0 0 22 22" fill="none">
            <rect x="2" y="4" width="18" height="14" rx="2" stroke="#CB9F5A" stroke-width="1.3"/>
            <path d="M3 5l8 7 8-7" stroke="#CB9F5A" stroke-width="1.3" stroke-linecap="round"/>
          </svg>
          <div>
            <div class="label">Email</div>
            <a href="mailto:cat@goldfin.group">cat@goldfin.group</a>
          </div>
        </div>
        <div class="reach-row">
          <svg width="22" height="22" viewBox="0 0 22 22" fill="none">
            <path d="M6 3H3c-.6 0-1 .5-1 1.1C2 12.3 9.7 20 17.9 20c.6 0 1.1-.4 1.1-1v-3c0-.5-.4-1-.9-1l-3.3-.6c-.4-.1-.8.1-1 .4l-1.2 1.6a13 13 0 01-5.7-5.7l1.6-1.2c.3-.2.5-.6.4-1L7.1 4c-.1-.5-.5-.9-1-1z" stroke="#CB9F5A" stroke-width="1.3" stroke-linejoin="round"/>
          </svg>
          <div>
            <div class="label">Phone</div>
            <a href="tel:+15054049970">505-404-9970</a>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>

    <div class="cta-row" style="margin:0 0 40px">
      <a class="btn btn-gold" href="/book">Book a 15-minute call</a>
      <span class="quiet">The simplest way to start.</span>
    </div>

    <div class="scarcity">
      <p>Because our relationships are built for the long term and run deep, we take on only a small number of clients at a time.</p>
      <p class="reach-line">We're glad to meet over Zoom to get acquainted — where you're located in the country is no concern of ours. The right fit matters more than the zip code.</p>
    </div>

    <p class="phase-label">The offices</p>

    <div class="contact-grid">
      <div class="office-card">
        <div class="city">Franklin, Tennessee</div>
        <div class="addr">231 Public Square, Suite 300
          <span>Franklin, TN 37064</span>
        </div>
      </div>
      <div class="office-card">
        <div class="city">Albuquerque, New Mexico</div>
        <div class="addr">2440 Louisiana Blvd NE, Suite 570
          <span>Albuquerque, NM 87110</span>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>

    <div class="director-note">
      <div class="dn-mark">&#8212;</div>
      <p>If you're an existing client, you already have a direct line to your team — no front desk, no phone tree. This page is simply where new conversations begin.</p>
    </div>

  </div>
</section>
</BaseLayout>
